    <abstract>Official romanization (ontop of the English title): “Taishō Daigaku Sōgōbukkyō Kenyūjo Sōsho”. This transcription has two major issues. First, the correct transcription of 研究所 would be Kenkyūjo (or Kenkyūsho), the editors however wrote “Kenyūjo” without a k. Second, the transcription omits the second “研究” and transcribes “Kenkyūjo Sōsho” for “研究所研究叢書”. Therefore, in this XML-file the missing k was added, but the second “Kenkyū” is omitted, just as in the original. Technically one might also separate “Sōgō” from “bukkyō” and write “Sōgō Bukkyō”, instead of “Sōgōbukkyō”, but this issue will be ignored.</abstract>
